\c 47 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 47\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Waaqayyo Guutummaa Biyya Lafaa Irratti Mootii Dha (Geggeessituu warra faarfatootaaf; faarfannaa ilmaan Qoraahi)
\m \bd 1\bd* Yaa saba garaa garaa hundumti keessan, harka keessan walitti rurrukutaa! Sagalee keessan ol fuudhaa, Waaqayyotti gammaduu keessan dhageessisaa.
\m \bd 2\bd* Waaqayyo inni hundumaa gararraa jiru sodaachisaa dha, inni guutummaa biyya lafaa irratti mootii guddaa dha.
\m \bd 3\bd* inni saba garaa garaa harka keenya jala in galche, namoota hundumaas miilla keenya jala kaa'e. 
\m \bd 4\bd* inni biyya dhaala keenyaa nuuf in fo'a, Yaaqoob inni Waaqayyo jaallatu biyyichaan in koora.
\m \bd 5\bd* Waaqayyo gooftaan sagalee gammachuutiin, sagalee fiinootiinis ol ba'eera.
\m \bd 6\bd* Waaqayyoon faarfannaadhaan jajadhaa! Isa faarfadhaa! Mootii keenya faarfannaadhaan jajadhaa! Isa faarfadhaa.
\m \bd 7\bd* Waaqayyo mootii guutummaa biyya lafaa waan ta'eef, isa faarfadhaa, mararoodhaan jajadhaa!
\m \bd 8\bd* Waaqayyo saba warra kaan irratti in mo'a, Waaqayyo teessoo isaa isa qulqulluu irra in taa'a.
\m \bd 9\bd* gurguddoonni saba garaa garaa, saba Waaqayyo isa kan Abrahaamitti dabalamanii, walitti sassaabamanii jiru, warri biyyaaf gaachana ta'an kan Waaqayyoo waan ta'aniif, inni guddaa ol kaafameera. 
\b 
